{"tid":2487450,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"富野由悠季：要打倒鬼滅EVA 連這心態都沒有就別想再做TV動畫","createTime":"2021-04-13T14:14:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-13T14:22:10.000Z","uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f7a809ff6f2d65616151be933dd96834ad22194e","tid":2487450,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T14:14:01.000Z","msg":"朝日電視台綜藝節目「林修の今でしょ！」，今日的2小時特番以現代動畫為討論主題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其中講了很多有關動畫製作鮮為大眾所知的冷知識，例如「光之美少女」的變身場景短短58秒，作畫枚數竟高達464枚；而「進擊的巨人」的全手繪動作場景，更被譽為改變日本動畫「傳說中的18秒」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n節目中最受關注的莫過於是高達之父富野由悠季監督的訪談，他對時下流行動畫現象的發言也讓觀眾們都大吃一驚。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">「要是能繼續活著做新作的話，當然想要把鬼滅之刃和EVA打倒。要是連這種心態都沒有，過了80歲就做不了TV動畫了。」</span><br />\n<br />\n年過80仍有這樣的鬥心和活力，讓主持和網民們深感佩服。如果和此前另一位動畫大師宮崎駿監督的態度比較，也是非常有趣的對比呢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/mainitiokiraku3/status/1381934946747514881?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmainitiokiraku3%2Fstatus%2F1381934946747514881%3Fs%3D21&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11PQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=aafc7161\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmainitiokiraku3%2Fstatus%2F1381934946747514881%3Fs%3D21&h=8acd9ba6\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/mainitiokiraku3/status/1381934946747514881?s=21</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/uvatmmtoffkigon/status/1381956702854029314?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fuvatmmtoffkigon%2Fstatus%2F1381956702854029314%3Fs%3D21&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11PQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=bca59181\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fuvatmmtoffkigon%2Fstatus%2F1381956702854029314%3Fs%3D21&h=8188233c\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/uvatmmtoffkigon/status/1381956702854029314?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/m5xcwadjwt2ayxk/status/1381935451297116160?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fm5xcwadjwt2ayxk%2Fstatus%2F13819